  <heading>BFSUB (unpredicated)</heading>
  <desc>
    <brief>
      <para>BFloat16 subtract (unpredicated)</para>
    </brief>
    <authored>
      <para>This instruction subtracts all BFloat16 elements of the second source vector from
corresponding BFloat16 elements of the first source vector and places
the results in the corresponding elements of the destination vector.</para>
      <para>This instruction follows SVE2 non-widening BFloat16 numerical behaviors.</para>
      <para>This instruction is unpredicated.</para>
      <para>ID_AA64ZFR0_EL1.B16B16 indicates whether this instruction is implemented.</para>
    </authored>
    <predicated>False</predicated>
  </desc>
